Respinte, then, to the sender the charges arrived from the Pd after the stop to the primary. "Schlein from the stage of Bari chose insults. I got used to it, you added to Renzi and Calenda that insult me every day. But - Count warns - I do not allow you to offend the citizens who helped build the M5s among the banquets, without having behind that media system that you enjoy as leader of the Pd". Are you going out of the Apulian junta? "I don't advance anything. We'll have a press conference on the theme for days. But, given this context, nothing can be more like before for us," says M5s leader.
<h2>"Schlein changes the PD as promised"</h2>
"Schlein changes the Pd as he promised, before the Pd changes her", is the message that, Giuseppe Conte then launches in an interview with "Il Corriere della Sera" after the break of the wide field in Puglia.
&nbsp;
The leader M5s rejects the charge of unfairness arrived by the secretary dem. "Beware of unfairness - he emphasizes - offends the people who created the M5S and who, since 2009, made the principle of legality our polar star. For us they are not at stake between parties or among leaders, the political substance is at stake. It is a question of renewing the ruling class to build something different from Italy that we do not like. We can't make spatters and this means being loyal to citizens."
&nbsp;
Conte then recalls that "if we have blown out the primaries of the progressive field after the investigations is because for us the fight against corruption and illegality is a non-negotiable heritage".
&nbsp;
To those who rebuke the Allied Movement with the Pd only when the candidate is of the M5s, Count reply: "It's the most ridiculous and cheating thing I'm told. Since we've been working with the PD in the territories, I think that 90% of the candidates in the local elections have the PD card." For the M5s leader, finally, "the fortunes of the progressive field area not only depend on us, but also on what Schlein will do. Do you want to pursue the commitments made with the community that invested her secretary, to transform the PD? Or will it be transformed by the Pd?"

